[SHORT DESC]
Deals 12.5% damage to sleeping opponents per turn. 
[LONG DESC]
<p>As long as this Pokémon is in play against a sleeping opponent, that opponent will take damage equal to 12.5% of its max HP at the end of each turn. This ability will deal damage even if the opponent is asleep due to Rest. In a double battle, if both enemies have Bad Dreams, a sleeping Pokémon will lose health due to Bad Dreams twice. A sleeping Pokémon will not lose health because of its partner's Bad Dreams.</p>